          <li><a href="/portfolio">Portfolio</a></li>
          <li><a href="/demos">Demos</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog">Blog</a></li>
          <li><a href="/resources">Resources</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-small">Get Quote</a></li>
        </ul>

        <button class="mobile-menu-btn" aria-label="Toggle menu">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/>
            <line x1="3" y1="12" x2="21" y2="12"/>
            <line x1="3" y1="18" x2="21" y2="18"/>
          </svg>
        </button>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Our Services</h1>
      <p>Everything you need to build, grow, and market your business online</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services Grid -->
  <section class="services-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="services-list">
        <!-- Web Design -->
        <a href="/services/web-design" class="service-item">
          <div class="service-icon-lg">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/>
              <line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="service-content">
            <h2>Web Design & Development</h2>
            <p>Custom websites that look stunning, work perfectly on all devices, and convert visitors into customers. From simple business sites to complex web applications.</p>
            <ul class="service-features">
              <li>Custom design tailored to your brand</li>
              <li>Mobile-first responsive development</li>
              <li>Fast loading speeds</li>
              <li>SEO-friendly structure</li>
            </ul>
            <span class="service-price">From $1,500</span>
            <span class="service-link">Learn More →</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- WordPress -->
        <a href="/services/wordpress" class="service-item">
          <div class="service-icon-lg">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/>
              <path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/>
              <path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="service-content">
            <h2>WordPress Development</h2>
            <p>Custom WordPress websites and WooCommerce stores that you can easily manage yourself. From blogs to full e-commerce solutions.</p>
            <ul class="service-features">
              <li>Custom theme development</li>
              <li>WooCommerce online stores</li>
              <li>Plugin customization</li>
              <li>Easy content management</li>
            </ul>
            <span class="service-price">From $2,000</span>
            <span class="service-link">Learn More →</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- E-commerce -->
        <a href="/services/ecommerce" class="service-item">
          <div class="service-icon-lg">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <circle cx="9" cy="21" r="1"/>
              <circle cx="20" cy="21" r="1"/>
              <path d="M1 1h4l2.68 13.39a2 2 0 0 0 2 1.61h9.72a2 2 0 0 0 2-1.61L23 6H6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="service-content">
            <h2>E-commerce Solutions</h2>
            <p>Start selling online with a professional e-commerce store. We set up everything you need to accept payments and manage orders.</p>
            <ul class="service-features">
              <li>WooCommerce & Shopify</li>
              <li>Payment gateway integration</li>
              <li>Inventory management</li>
              <li>Shipping & tax setup</li>
            </ul>
            <span class="service-price">From $6,000</span>
            <span class="service-link">Learn More →</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Odoo -->
        <a href="/services/odoo" class="service-item">
          <div class="service-icon-lg" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #714B67 0%, #875A7B 100%);">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
              <path d="M8 12h8"/>
              <path d="M12 8v8"/>
              <path d="M8 8l8 8"/>
              <path d="M16 8l-8 8"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="service-content">
            <h2>Odoo Implementation</h2>
            <p>All-in-one business management platform combining website, e-commerce, CRM, inventory, and accounting. Perfect for growing businesses wanting to eliminate data silos.</p>
            <ul class="service-features">
              <li>Integrated business suite</li>
              <li>Website + E-commerce</li>
              <li>CRM & Sales automation</li>
              <li>Inventory & Accounting</li>
            </ul>
            <span class="service-price">From $5,000</span>
            <span class="service-link">Learn More →</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- SEO -->
        <a href="/services/seo" class="service-item">
          <div class="service-icon-lg">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/>
              <line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/>
              <path d="M11 8v6"/>
              <path d="M8 11h6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="service-content">
            <h2>SEO Services</h2>
            <p>Get found on Google with our proven SEO strategies. We help Sydney businesses rank higher and attract more organic traffic.</p>
            <ul class="service-features">
              <li>Keyword research & strategy</li>
              <li>On-page optimization</li>
              <li>Local SEO for Sydney</li>
              <li>Monthly reporting</li>
            </ul>
            <span class="service-price">From $500/mo</span>
            <span class="service-link">Learn More →</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Google Ads -->
        <a href="/services/sem" class="service-item">
          <div class="service-icon-lg">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/>
              <path d="M3 9h18"/>
              <path d="M9 21V9"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="service-content">
            <h2>Google Ads Management</h2>
            <p>Get immediate results with professionally managed Google Ads campaigns. We maximize your ROI with targeted advertising.</p>
            <ul class="service-features">
              <li>Campaign setup & management</li>
              <li>Keyword targeting</li>
              <li>Ad copywriting</li>
              <li>Conversion tracking</li>
            </ul>
            <span class="service-price">From $400/mo + ad spend</span>
            <span class="service-link">Learn More →</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Hosting & Maintenance -->
        <a href="/services/hosting" class="service-item">
          <div class="service-icon-lg">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="8" rx="2" ry="2"/>
              <rect x="2" y="14" width="20" height="8" rx="2" ry="2"/>
              <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="6.01" y2="6"/>
              <line x1="6" y1="18" x2="6.01" y2="18"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="service-content">
            <h2>Hosting & Maintenance</h2>
            <p>Keep your website secure, fast, and up-to-date with our managed hosting and maintenance packages.</p>
            <ul class="service-features">
              <li>Fast Australian hosting</li>
              <li>Daily backups</li>
              <li>Security monitoring</li>
              <li>Regular updates</li>
            </ul>
            <span class="service-price">From $50/mo</span>
            <span class="service-link">Learn More →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta section-navy">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Not Sure What You Need?</h2>
        <p>Book a free consultation and we'll help you create a digital strategy for your business.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-white btn-large">Get Free Consultation</a>
